overview: A definitive documentary revisiting the legendary record label of the 70's, Casablanca Records, featuring exclusive interviews with the executives behind the scenes that made Casablanca Records a worldwide phenomenon.Interviews include Susan Munao, Norby Walters, Richard Trugman, Arthur Kassel, and many more. Also including unreleased footage,videos, and news stories.
